  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its height, scale, and massing, has the potential to result in a loss of light and a poor outlook for the occupiers of the adjoining premises, with no BRE sunlight/daylight study submitted to demonstrate otherwise. As such, the proposal is contrary to LP33 policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) (2020), policy D6 (Housing quality and standards) of The London Plan (2021), and Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development would result in the provision of substandard accommodation for the occupiers of the basement flat in terms of poor light and outlook for the proposed living/dining/kitchen area and the 2 new bedrooms, to the detriment of the long term health and well being of the occupiers of the development, contrary to policy D6 (Housing quality and standards) of The London Plan (2021), and policies LP1 (&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Design Quality and Local Character)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;LP17 (Housing Design Standards) of the Hackney Local Plan LP33 (2020) and Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-adf2f5ad-7fff-3213-576d-27c26ce2e7df&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed rear extension, by reason of its size, positioning, and required foundations, has the potential to adversely affect the root protection zones (RPZ) and canopies of trees located within the site and neighbouring gardens, and no tree survey or arboriculture report has been submitted to demonstrate otherwise. As such, the proposal is contrary to policies LP51 (Tree Management and Landscaping) and LP47 (&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-82c5b103-7fff-2e12-5a78-9319636f6937&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Biodiversity and Sites of Importance of Nature Conservation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) of LP33 (2020) and policies&amp;nbsp;G5 (Urban greening), G6 (Biodiversity and access to nature), and G7 (Trees and woodlands) of The London Plan (2020).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-f06e718e-7fff-19e2-7070-e8b07f86a1dc&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;"
  ],
